新娘送礼会礼物、登记处婚礼登记处，蓝色 (3065-BL)" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>59.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="get-weird-with-it">变得很奇怪</h2><p>嘿，如果你没有什么可失去的，为什么不大摇大摆呢？</p><ul><li><p><strong>可微波炉加热的拖鞋。</strong>寒冷日子的终极舒适礼物。加热后美味可口！只是在开玩笑。请不要吃它们。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/aXdyMB?pageview_type=RSS&amp;amp%3Btemplate=Roundups&amp;amp%3Bmodule=content-body&amp;amp%3Belement=offer&amp;amp%3Bitem=text-link&amp;amp%3Belement_label=Available%20for%20%2430.99&amp;amp%3Bshort_url=aXdyMB&amp;amp%3Bu=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbest-secret-santa-gift-ideas&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Available%20for%20%2430.99&amp;short_url=aXdyMB&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>售价 30.99 美元</u></a>。</p></li><li><p><strong>减压挤压玩具</strong>。可爱又实用的压力消除器。请务必与疲惫的同事们分享对此的了解。这款<a href="https://zdcs.link/ak7ymn?pageview_type=RSS&amp;amp%3Btemplate=Roundups&amp;amp%3Bmodule=content-body&amp;amp%3Belement=offer&amp;amp%3Bitem=text-link&amp;amp%3Belement_label=fidget%20toy%20for%20adults%20is%20%2424.99&amp;amp%3Bshort_url=ak7ymn&amp;amp%3Bu=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbest-secret-santa-gift-ideas&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=fidget%20toy%20for%20adults%20is%20%2424.99&amp;short_url=ak7ymn&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>成人烦躁玩具售价 24.99 美元</u></a>，或者更傻的“calma llama”售价<a href="https://zdcs.link/avxyVx?pageview_type=RSS&amp;amp%3Btemplate=Roundups&amp;amp%3Bmodule=content-body&amp;amp%3Belement=offer&amp;amp%3Bitem=text-link&amp;amp%3Belement_label=%2413.99&amp;amp%3Bshort_url=avxyVx&amp;amp%3Bu=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbest-secret-santa-gift-ideas&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=%2413.99&amp;short_url=avxyVx&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>13.99 美元</u></a>。</p></li><li><p> <strong>LED 蓝牙无檐小便帽</strong>。对于礼物交换来说，这是一个很棒的举动：非常适合音乐爱好者、寒冷的天气，并且它满足了对独特物品的需求。我的意思是，如果有人自愿拥有其中一件，我会感到震惊。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/9lwyDX?pageview_type=RSS&amp;amp%3Btemplate=Roundups&amp;amp%3Bmodule=content-body&amp;amp%3Belement=offer&amp;amp%3Bitem=text-link&amp;amp%3Belement_label=Get%20one%20for%20%2419.99&amp;amp%3Bshort_url=9lwyDX&amp;amp%3Bu=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbest-secret-santa-gift-ideas&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Get%20one%20for%20%2430.99&amp;short_url=9lwyDX&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>仅需 30.99 美元即可购买一件</u></a>。</p></li></ul><p>为了了解更多，我收集了一些更<a href="https://lifehacker.com/entertainment/best-secret-santa-gift-ideas" target="_blank">古怪的礼物，这些礼物在这里并不糟糕</a>。</p><h2 id="charitable-donations">慈善捐款</h2><p>以某人的名义捐赠的慈善捐款对于行善者和热衷于社会事业的人们来说可能是有意义的。您可以通过各种非营利组织选择货币金额或象征性地收养动物或树木。打印一份定制证书，交给接受者，宣布您为纪念他们而捐款。</p><p> Lifehacker 总编辑<a href="https://lifehacker.com/author/meghanwalbert" target="_blank">Meghan Walbert</a>推荐<a href="https://zdcs.link/JyZon?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=One%20Simple%20Wish&amp;short_url=JyZon&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">One Simple Wish</a> ，这是一个允许您为寄养儿童实现愿望的组织。另一种选择是以某人的名义种一棵树， <a href="https://zdcs.link/prp14?pageview_type=RSS&amp;template=content&amp;module=content_body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=which%20you%20can%20do%20here&amp;short_url=prp14&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">您可以在此处执行此操作</a>。</p><p>嘿，如果他们对慈善礼物很讨厌，那么他们首先应该反思一下为什么他们这么难买礼物。但希望，通过一点额外的深思熟虑和创造力，你可以让假期购物清单上最挑剔的东西变得亮起来。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/money/gifts-for-the-person-who-has-everything<dc:creator>梅雷迪思·迪茨</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category></item></channel></rss>